<h2>Usage Notes:</h2>
<ul>
<li>Acceptable variables are: <code>a</code>, <code>b</code>, ..., <code>z<=
/code>.</li>
<li>Acceptable connectives are: <code>~</code> (not), <code>&amp;</code> (a=
nd), <code>|</code> (or), <code>&gt;</code> (implication), <code>=3D</code>=
 (equivalence), <code>0</code> (false), <code>1</code> (true), listed in or=
der of operator precedence.</li>
<li>Use parenthesis to manually specify precedence, e.g., <a href=3D"https:=
